===Noun===
{{en-noun|pervert|perverts}}

#One who has been perverted; one who has turned to [[error]].
#A sexually perverted person.

====Usage notes====
*In contemporary usage, '''pervert''' is usually understood to refer to a [[sexual]]ly perverted person. Traditionally the word was mainly associated with persons of [[false]] [[religious]] [[belief]]s.

====Synonyms====
